.TH TGLFS-DELETE 1 "March 2026" "tglfs 0.1.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tglfs-delete \- delete one or more owned TGLFS files from Saved Messages
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tglfs delete
[\fB--yes\fR] [\fB--no-interactive\fR] [\fB--json\fR] \fIufids...\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
Deletes the Saved Messages file card plus all referenced chunk messages for each UFID.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --yes
Skip the confirmation prompt.
.TP
.B --no-interactive
Disable interactive prompts and fail instead of prompting.
.TP
.B --json
Emit machine-readable JSON.
.SH AI AGENT NOTES
Agents should pass
.B --yes
in non-interactive or JSON sessions.
